CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 22, 1961, pg. A13, reads: "In Concert - Among the participants in the concert celebrating the 30th anniversary of the Norris Music Club, at Stephen Foster Memorial Hall, were the above artists. Left to right: Miriam Kelly, soprano; Richard Beasley, pianist; Vivian Reid, soprano; Alfred Morris, violinist, and Cynthia Darrett, accompanist. Robert Mosley, baritone (top center), was the guest soloist. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Musicians for concert presented by Norris Music Club, soprano Miriam Kelly, pianist Richard Beasley, soprano Vivian Reid, violinist Alfred Morris, accompanist Cynthia Darrett, and baritone Robert Mosley or Mosely in back, posed in Stephen Foster Memorial Hall
